data.description: Welcome home to this updated three-bedroom home with lots of updates in a convenient Russellville location. The home has new LVP flooring throughout, new light fixtures and clean, modern paint colors. The convenient layout sees the kitchen flow seamlessly into the living space with all three bedrooms on the other side of the home.   This home sits on nearly one acre of land, with a fully fenced-in backyard. The landscaping was just updated with brand new river rocks and shrubbery. The roof was replaced this past summer.
